# Walkthrough - Phase 8: Debugging & Fixes

We have successfully resolved all compilation errors and launched the **Gemini Launcher**.

## Key Fixes Implemented

### 1. UI Compilation (XAML)
- **Namespace Errors (`MC3074`)**: Replaced `ui:NavigationView.Content` (deprecated/removed in newer WPF UI) with `ui:NavigationView.ContentOverlay` to correctly host the `Frame`.
- **Property Errors (`MC3072`)**:
    - Replaced standard WPF `Button` with `ui:Button` in [HomePage.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/HomePage.xaml), [DownloadPage.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/DownloadPage.xaml), and [SettingsPage.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/SettingsPage.xaml) to support the `Appearance="Primary/Secondary"` property.
    - Removed `PlaceholderText` from standard `ComboBox` (invalid property) and `TextBox` (migrated to `ui:TextBox` or `PlaceholderText` supported controls).
    - Removed `Spacing` property from standard `StackPanel` (invalid property) and used `Margin` instead.
- **Resource Errors (`MC3050`)**: Added `BooleanToVisibilityConverter` to [ResourcesPage.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/ResourcesPage.xaml) resources to fix binding errors.

### 2. Logic & Service Fixes (C#)
- **ModpackService**: Fixed a constructor mismatch (CS7036) by removing an unused [InstallationService](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/InstallationService.cs#12-193) dependency.
- **MainViewModel**: Renamed a local variable `analyzer` to `crashAnalyzer` to resolve a shadowing conflict (CS0136).
- **DownloadService**: Added a missing helper method [DownloadStringAsync](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Network/DownloadService.cs#40-44) (CS1061) required by [InstallationService](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/InstallationService.cs#12-193).
- **Models**:
    - Fixed a syntax error in [ModFile.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Models/Ecosystem/ModFile.cs) (CS1022).
    - Added the missing `GameVersions` property to [ModFile](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Models/Ecosystem/ModFile.cs#5-18) class (CS0117), which was being populated by [ModrinthService](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Ecosystem/ModrinthService.cs#11-141).

